Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=16}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.90,0:01:55.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é demais!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Tô contando com vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.64,0:02:03.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's amazing that such a convenient\Ncreature exists in this world. - OG}{Who would've thought such a convenient creature exists in this world. - Z}Quem diria que essas criaturas\Npoderiam ser tão úteis!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a pretty smooth ride, isn't it? I'm getting used to it! - OG}A viagem é bem tranquila. Confortável também!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.80,0:02:08.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra direita! Direita!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The ball is coming your way! OK, throw it! - OG}A bola tá indo pra vocês! Lá vai!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't let it go into the canal! - OG}Ah! Segura a bola!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.66,0:02:22.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Passa a bola! Passa a bola!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.25,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Que massa!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This looks like a residential area. - OG}Parece uma área residencial.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.69,0:02:35.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa cidade com certeza foi construída\Npensando nos canais.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.10,0:02:48.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, tem uma subida. Será que a gente consegue\Nir contra a correnteza?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente consegue subir?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.39,0:02:58.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Caminho errado! Vai pra direita! Direita!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.49,0:03:02.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles conseguem até subir morro\Ncontra a água, hein?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.23,0:03:03.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nada mal, vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem canais até nos telhados!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.79,0:03:14.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas a gente tá indo pro caminho errado!\NPrecisamos ir pro distrito comercial primeiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh? What's the hurry? - OG}Ah? Qual é a pressa?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.15,0:03:20.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é todo dia que a gente pode\Npassear pelos canais.
Comment: 5,0:03:20.34,0:03:20.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Hm?\N– Hm?
Comment: 5,0:03:20.89,0:03:21.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei! O-Olha! Olha pra frente!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.13,0:03:29.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade! A gente tá no topo da colina!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que... significa que...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente tá voando!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tamo caindo. Tamo caindo.\NTamo caindo. Tamo caindo.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.78,0:03:53.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tamo caindo. Tamo caindo. Tamo caindo.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.79,0:03:58.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Tamo caindo!\N– Tamo caindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.00,0:04:09.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não seja tão imprudente!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.69,0:04:14.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Moça! Nossos produtos são baratos!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.49,0:04:20.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que tal dar uma olhada nos nossos produtos?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Temos muitos itens raros e de qualidade!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.58,0:04:30.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Começando agora nossa promoção de 50% de desconto!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Esse lugar ficou animado!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ué? A gente foi parar no distrito comercial!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então o caminho que você pegou era um atalho?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.88,0:04:45.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa! Vocês são bem espertos, afinal!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.42,0:04:49.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nunca estive num distrito comercial\Ntão animado!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, olha isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse touro é enorme!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caramba! Ei, ele tá vindo pra cá!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse bicho é assustador!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele ia engolir a gente inteiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que é tamanho gigante?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? O que há com eles?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Máscaras...?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau, são tão elegantes!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que é algum tipo de festa?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? O que tá acontecendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.09,0:05:24.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venham comprar!\NTakoyaki hidroaquecido, fresquinho!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, são dois croquetes hidro?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.01,0:05:32.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os dois parecem deliciosos! Yagara, vai pra lá.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Que ideia é essa?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy! Onde você tá indo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pergunta pro yagara!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo! O que vai ser?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.28,0:05:51.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, então você estava com fome.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.49,0:05:56.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Apesar de ser normalmente para pessoas,\Na carne hidro é a comida favorita dos yagaras.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hidro? Então me dá dez!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São tão boas que os cozinheiros da\NCidade Gourmet compram em segredo.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.99,0:06:05.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Satisfaz o corpo e a alma, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.30,0:06:13.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São... tão... macias!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.10,0:06:13.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Delícia!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.94,0:06:17.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! É tão bom assim?!\NEi, Luffy! Joga uma pra cá!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Vai comprar a sua!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Nami! Leva o barco até aquela loja!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.60,0:06:28.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais máscaras? Parecem estar por toda a cidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E as pessoas usando as máscaras...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Nami!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.34,0:06:42.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para a última parte da viagem até a Ilha do Estaleiro,\Nvamos subir por um elevador de comporta.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um elevador de comporta?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É aquela coisa que parece uma torre.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entrem, por favor!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.77,0:07:02.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O elevador leva até a Ilha do Estaleiro,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.73,0:07:10.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,onde ficam os estaleiros\Ne o centro de Water Seven!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, entrem pela comporta!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.09,0:07:17.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um minuto até fechar!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vai acontecer lá dentro?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caramba! Fecharam a comporta atrás de nós!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tamo subindo!\NTamo subindo! Tamo subindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.56,0:07:41.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendi. Isso acontece. Aí isso acontece.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.40,0:07:44.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aí é isso e aquilo,\No que faz ser um elevador de comporta.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.52,0:07:48.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Water Seven é bem legal!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.89,0:07:52.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então eles usam água pra tudo!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem você tá chamando de "cabeça de musgo"?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Zoro.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê a Robin? Ela não tá no navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.51,0:08:16.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É mesmo. Ela e o Chopper\Nsaíram mais cedo.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.97,0:08:17.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela disse que ia fazer compras.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.54,0:08:24.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso?! Então você é\No único no navio?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que decepção!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode crer.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza, então. Vou fazer as compras.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cuida do navio enquanto eu tô fora.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Putz, ele já dormiu.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tanto faz. Ela é toda sua.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chegamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.20,0:09:25.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então esse é o centro de Water Seven\Ne o maior estaleiro do mundo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que tem mais terra\Ndo que água por aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tudo é tão enorme!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nunca vi uma cidade tão grande!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é aquela multidão?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:57.60,0:09:59.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estão olhando o estaleiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.60,0:10:03.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver! Vai, yagara!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.00,0:10:14.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, olha ali!\NÉ o Lucci! Ele é tão bonito!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Paulie não tá aqui?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.49,0:10:22.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Lulu tá aqui! Tão elegante!\NEle é realmente um homem de verdade.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas ninguém é mais viril que o Tilestone!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, moço.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.56,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aconteceu alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.15,0:10:35.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, uns piratas tentaram causar\Nproblema no Dock One de novo.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.70,0:10:40.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas acabou com os artesãos\Nderrubando eles, como sempre.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem fim pra esses idiotas.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.07,0:10:45.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os carpinteiros conseguem bater em piratas?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, você deve ser um marinheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.01,0:10:51.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela multidão... Bom, são só curiosos.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.38,0:10:57.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo por aqui admira\Nos carpinteiros da Galley-La Company.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são fortes...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e habilidosos.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São o orgulho de Water Seven.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Mal posso esperar pra conhecê-los!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.19,0:11:17.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos logo pro\Ncâmbio de moedas.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente volta aqui depois.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o distrito comercial dos Becos.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.89,0:11:40.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chamam um lugar tão animado de Becos?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.90,0:11:43.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem lugares pra andar a pé também, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Água limpa que combina com uma cidade impecável...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! O que é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É uma loja de máscaras.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.86,0:12:00.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Notei que as pessoas andam\Npela cidade usando essas máscaras.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.30,0:12:04.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, eles estão de máscara?\NEu achei que tinham caras estranhas.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.85,0:12:10.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que San Faldo está\Nfazendo um festival de fantasias.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.49,0:12:13.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É uma ilha que dá pra chegar\Nusando o Sea Train.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.25,0:12:16.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Como você sabe disso?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As pessoas passando estão falando sobre isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fico surpreso que você consiga ouvir elas.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um hábito.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.90,0:12:29.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desde criança, eu sobrevivi ouvindo\Nos que estavam ao meu redor e sentindo as intenções.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é incrível, Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Doutor...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ali! É uma livraria.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Podemos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Claro! Vamos entrar.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eba!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou do CP9.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin! Eu vou entrar, tá?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.14,0:13:59.15,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ser tranquilo na minha forma humana.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.65,0:14:05.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau, que máscara legal!\NDo que você tá fantasiado?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.39,0:14:08.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, sabe... Um reno humano.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que bom que está se divertindo.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.59,0:14:16.54,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pensamos em pegar vocês dormindo.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.59,0:15:14.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem são vocês, esquisitos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.50,0:15:16.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se identifiquem!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.93,0:15:20.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C-Cem milhões de berry?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I-Idiota! Você é muito alto!\NTodo mundo tá ouvindo!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.37,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,V-V-Vocês vão nos dar tudo isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.37,0:15:29.86,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,T-Ti-Tipo... Como eu disse, Luffy, você é muito alto!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso realmente vale tudo isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.91,0:15:36.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é um ouro incrivelmente puro\Ncom significado histórico.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com essa grana,\Na gente pode consertar a Merry de verdade!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.99,0:15:42.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É! E ainda vai sobrar!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Legal! Então a gente usa o resto\Npra comprar uma estátua de bronze!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não. Não, a gente não vai.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.78,0:15:51.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se aceitar esse valor, por favor assine\Ne coloque sua impressão digital aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.14,0:15:54.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou preparar o dinheiro imediatamente.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.22,0:15:57.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Eu coloco quantas\Nimpressões digitais você quiser!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se não bastar, eu coloco a minha também!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.65,0:16:12.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera. O que houve, Nami?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.31,0:16:17.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho três coisas\Npra dizer, Sr. Avaliador.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Primeiro...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.58,0:16:23.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esqueci de mencionar que esse cara tem\Numa recompensa de 100 milhões de berry pela cabeça.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Segundo...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.75,0:16:30.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A avaliação que você acabou\Nde nos dar é inaceitável.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.09,0:16:33.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Terceiro... Se mentir pra gente de novo...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.01,0:16:36.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,sua cabeça é nossa.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor...!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.52,0:16:41.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, me perdoe!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.39,0:16:46.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,T-Trezentos milhões de berry?!\NEu não tô sonhando, né?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.40,0:16:50.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossa aventura na Ilha do Céu\Nfinalmente valeu a pena!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou super rico!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Você quis dizer "nós"!\N– Você quis dizer "nós"!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,P-Por favor, voltem sempre!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.80,0:17:01.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,V-V-V-Virou 300 milhões! E-Eu tô com medo!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tô carregando 100 milhões?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.66,0:17:07.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caramba, a Nami é muito boa\Nem fazer ameaças assustadoras, hein?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.44,0:17:11.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu já estimei mais ou menos esse valor\Ndesde o começo, mas aí ele falou "100 milhões".
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.70,0:17:14.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês dois não conseguiram disfarçar,\Nentão ele tentou nos enganar.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy! Você não devia\Nficar balançando isso assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.51,0:17:22.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, de qualquer forma, que bom que deu certo.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.48,0:17:26.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Ahh! O rio!\N– Ahh! O rio!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos perder 100 milhões de berry pro rio!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ufa! Essa foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou te nocautear!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.01,0:17:41.09,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou quebrar seus dentes, seu idiota!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.19,0:17:46.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Eu... Eu sinto muito.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Se identifiquem"?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caçador de Piratas Zoro...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Somos caçadores de recompensas cujo nome\Nfaz até criança parar de chorar—
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a Família Franky!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.64,0:18:20.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua cabeça vale 60 milhões!\NVamos aceitar com prazer.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.98,0:18:23.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aí, vamos esperar em emboscada no navio...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.91,0:18:26.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e pegar a tripulação toda de uma vez.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.49,0:18:30.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos faturar alto! Que sorte!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.78,0:18:33.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o primeiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Sorte"?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês quiseram dizer azar, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fiquem firmes!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Two-Sword Style:
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.72,0:18:58.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rhino Cycle!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.51,0:19:11.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Imbecis.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.92,0:19:21.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,D-D-Diz, Nami... Talvez a gente devesse\Nlevar de volta pro navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ia ser perda de tempo.\NO estaleiro é logo depois dessa colina.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, eu tô um pouco chateado que vocês\Nnão me deixam chegar perto do dinheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando encontrarmos um carpinteiro,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.25,0:19:37.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vamos ter que voltar pra Merry com ele\Nna hora pra fazer o orçamento do conserto.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz sentido.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.78,0:19:44.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente não sei como agir.\NNunca carreguei tanta grana.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.90,0:19:47.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, isso é natural.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que não é natural é alguém ficando balançando isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.86,0:19:52.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ei, olha ali!\NTão vendendo pãezinhos hidro!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos comprar 100!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.38,0:19:54.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Cala a boca.\N– Cala a boca.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então vamos comprar 1.000!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.01,0:19:55.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Cala a boca.\N– Cala a boca.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.70,0:19:56.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Cala a boca!\N– Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,T-Tá bom...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.69,0:20:15.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chegamos... de volta na entrada do estaleiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.60,0:20:22.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom! Parece que a multidão\Nde antes já foi embora.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.61,0:20:27.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enfim, vamos encontrar... hm... é...\NQual era o nome dele mesmo?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo! Icecara!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem será que ele é...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A velha senhora da estação disse pra falar com ele.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, disse sim...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.59,0:20:42.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais importante,\Na gente pode simplesmente entrar?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô entrando!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.41,0:20:45.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– De novo não!\N– De novo não!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.80,0:20:49.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.06,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Calma aí.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é daqui?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.77,0:20:56.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nesse caso, vamos conversar lá fora.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.37,0:21:01.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Apenas pessoas autorizadas\Npodem circular pelo estaleiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Opa.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.83,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,Tem algum assunto neste dock?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é o Usopp.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.60,0:21:16.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Eu tô bem aqui, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Verdade! O nariz é meio quadrado!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é! Hm...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gostaríamos de ver o Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.69,0:21:26.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sr. Iceburg, é? Vocês são clientes?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.96,0:21:28.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, é óbvio.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.70,0:21:32.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece ser uma indicação da\Nvovó Kokoro da Shift Station.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.06,0:21:35.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...? Você é velho ou algo assim?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.09,0:21:36.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho vinte e três anos.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.80,0:21:40.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra alguém de vinte e três anos\Nvocê fala como um velhote.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.96,0:21:43.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As pessoas sempre me dizem isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.29,0:21:45.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, você conhece esse tal de Iceburg?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.90,0:21:51.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conhecer? Ora, o Sr. Iceburg\Né o prefeito de Water Seven.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.87,0:21:55.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã... Então ele é um figurão.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.71,0:22:02.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não é só prefeito, é o presidente da\NGalley-La Company e administra o Sea Train.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele é o chefão daqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:04.10,0:22:07.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ora, em Water Seven, não há\Numa alma que não o conheça.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde a gente vai pra encontrar ele?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... Onde encontrá-lo agora...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:12.72,0:22:17.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele está sempre circulando por aí,\No que torna difícil encontrá-lo.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:17.19,0:22:20.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Você não pode entrar em contato com ele pra gente?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.67,0:22:23.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que é possível... O assunto é urgente?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é que a gente esteja com pressa, mas...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:27.11,0:22:31.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essencialmente, vocês ansiosos querem falar\Nsobre consertar o navio, certo?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde vocês ancoraram?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:33.92,0:22:35.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... Num lugar chamado Cabo Rochoso.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:35.70,0:22:40.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo. Vou dar um pulo lá\Ne avaliar a condição do navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.95,0:22:44.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai economizar tempo quando vocês falarem\Ncom o Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês podem discutir o preço do conserto também.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.88,0:22:50.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Dar um pulo"? Tipo, num touro yagara?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.39,0:22:56.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se eu fizer isso, vocês vão esperar\Numa eternidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dez minutos, e eu volto.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:58.44,0:23:00.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dez minutos?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.44,0:23:03.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Precisamente. Dez minutos.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.51,0:23:07.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caramba!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Ele é rápido!\N– C-Caramba!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.56,0:23:14.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oof!}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.83,0:23:17.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! Ele pulou!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Mas espera! Ali...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:23.25,0:23:24.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– ...é um precipício!\N– ...é um precipício!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:24.67,0:23:26.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele caiu!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:35.60,0:23:37.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:37.31,0:23:39.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:39.79,0:23:41.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele corre...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:41.02,0:23:43.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,livremente pela cidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?\N– O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:44.28,0:23:44.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conhecido como o Vento da Montanha...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.61,0:23:52.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ele é um dos encarregados do\NDock One da Galley-La Company:
Dialogue: 5,0:23:54.87,0:23:55.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kaku.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:00.00,0:24:03.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, bom. Entendo.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:03.79,0:24:07.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Cidade da Água... Isso é incrível!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:08.22,0:24:12.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nascentes e rios cristalinos...\NRuas limpas e multidões animadas...
Dialogue: 5,0:24:12.70,0:24:15.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E muitas mulheres bonitas!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:15.19,0:24:20.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quero levar a Nami ou a Robin\Npra sair numa cidade assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:20.77,0:24:23.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ter uma beleza em cada braço\Ntambém seria bom.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:26.29,0:24:29.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse lado é a Nami, e esse lado é a Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:29.60,0:24:31.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, moço.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:31.24,0:24:32.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para de fazer essa cara estranha.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:32.90,0:24:35.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, qual repolho hidro você vai comprar?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:35.50,0:24:37.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual...? Ah, sim, vou levar os dois.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:37.87,0:24:39.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, e senhora...
Dialogue: 5,0:24:39.80,0:24:43.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tô procurando a comida da estação\Ndessa cidade... O que tem disponível?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:43.83,0:24:47.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa ver. Hã? Que isso?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:47.09,0:24:49.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, não é tão fácil\Nandar por aqui a pé.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:52.78,0:24:55.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Outro beco sem saída? Que saco.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:55.94,0:24:58.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu me perdi? Isso não é bom.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:58.93,0:25:02.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso parece muito com um certo espadachim burro.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:02.49,0:25:03.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:09.32,0:25:12.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:13.00,0:25:18.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oi! Sou eu! Ei!\NRobin meu am– Ah, uh... Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:18.61,0:25:20.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso...?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:21.81,0:25:23.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela desapareceu...
Dialogue: 5,0:25:23.50,0:25:25.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,sem portas nem passarelas...?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:26.88,0:25:29.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela voou ou algo assim?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:29.29,0:25:29.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:33.08,0:25:34.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp...?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:35.40,0:25:40.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa cidade é meio estranha.\NOu sou eu que tô estranho?
Dialogue: 5,0:25:52.69,0:25:56.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ora, esse deve ser o navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:59.71,0:26:00.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com licença.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:04.34,0:26:06.87,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é só o Usopp.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:06.87,0:26:10.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo. Está danificado.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:15.11,0:26:17.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O mastro também precisa ser trocado.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:19.30,0:26:21.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp...?
Dialogue: 5,0:26:22.56,0:26:25.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera aí! Quem diabos é você?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:25.71,0:26:28.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, me perdoe. Interrompi sua soneca.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:29.24,0:26:31.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Putz! Que susto!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:31.68,0:26:33.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele pulou de lá!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:33.94,0:26:37.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom... meus carpinteiros\Nnão são nada comuns.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:37.53,0:26:39.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, quem é esse cara?
Dialogue: 5,0:26:39.01,0:26:39.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sei lá.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:39.89,0:26:43.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se alguém deseja construir rapidamente\Num navio mais rápido e mais capaz,
Dialogue: 5,0:26:43.69,0:26:46.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,habilidades físicas comuns simplesmente não servem.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:46.80,0:26:48.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kalifa, antes de começarmos...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:48.09,0:26:49.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu já verifiquei.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:50.81,0:26:55.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy,\NCaçador de Piratas Zoro, Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 5,0:26:56.42,0:26:59.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Três membros da tripulação têm recompensas.
Dialogue: 5,0:26:59.09,0:27:01.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recompensa total: 239 milhões de berry.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:01.99,0:27:03.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fundada no East Blue.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:03.43,0:27:07.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conhecidos como os Chapéus de Palha,\Ntripulação de sete membros.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:07.09,0:27:09.39,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Eles sabem tudo sobre nós.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:09.39,0:27:11.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo. Que bom que vieram.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:11.45,0:27:14.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Iceburg, o chefe desta cidade.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:14.40,0:27:17.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E este é um rato que eu encontrei antes.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:17.40,0:27:19.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O nome dele é... deixa ver...
Dialogue: 5,0:27:19.50,0:27:21.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tyrannosaurus.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:21.32,0:27:23.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso preparar a comida e a gaiola dele.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:23.30,0:27:25.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já está tudo pronto, Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:25.70,0:27:27.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, isso é bem a cara da Kalifa.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:27.33,0:27:29.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, senhor.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:29.60,0:27:30.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para seu conhecimento,
Dialogue: 5,0:27:30.55,0:27:34.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,em dez minutos, o senhor tem um jantar com um\Nexecutivo de vidraçaria no hotel em Chiza.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:34.95,0:27:37.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Depois disso, fará um discurso na Praça Liguria.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:37.59,0:27:41.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando acabar, tem uma conferência com\No Prefeito Bimine de Pucci, a Cidade Gourmet.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:41.95,0:27:44.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O jornal deles também vai entrevistá-lo.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:44.76,0:27:49.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por fim, precisará voltar ao escritório\Npara terminar um pouco de papelada.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:50.12,0:27:51.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:52.44,0:27:54.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito bem. Vou cancelar tudo.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:54.73,0:27:56.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Pode fazer isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:56.65,0:28:00.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com toda essa influência, eu posso\Nfazer isso de vez em quando.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:00.23,0:28:03.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é completamente inapto pra ser prefeito.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:03.30,0:28:05.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que egoísmo!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:05.51,0:28:08.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então esse cara é aquele que\Na velhinha falou?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:08.80,0:28:10.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, é ele.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:10.62,0:28:12.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que descaramento!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:19.40,0:28:21.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que fez isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:21.00,0:28:22.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu Deus!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:28.23,0:28:31.24,Main-207+,,0,0,12,,Como ousa se referir a um dos
Dialogue: 5,0:28:31.24,0:28:33.48,Main-207+,,0,0,12,,melhores carpinteiros do mundo como "esse cara" ou "ele"!?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:33.48,0:28:34.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:28:34.98,0:28:37.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A secretária Kalifa teve\Numa de suas raras explosões!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:37.55,0:28:38.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero levar um chute dela também.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:38.98,0:28:42.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me perdoe. Perdi a\Ncompostura por um momento.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:42.49,0:28:46.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, o Sr. Iceburg é uma celebridade local.\NPor favor, tenham modos.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:46.91,0:28:49.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenta não deixar a Kalifa nervosa.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:49.54,0:28:51.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando ela fica nervosa...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:51.16,0:28:53.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ela não faz distinção.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:54.91,0:28:57.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela chutou o próprio chefe também!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:57.13,0:28:58.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenha modos você!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:58.88,0:29:02.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, mas enfim, o senhor é o Sr. Iceburg, certo?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:03.26,0:29:05.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, olhe isso. É uma indicação.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:05.34,0:29:07.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Da vovó Kokoro...?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:07.90,0:29:10.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Dê uma olhada no navio deles", hm...?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:11.00,0:29:12.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:12.31,0:29:16.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Não vai?! Por favor!\NPor favor, conserte nosso navio!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:16.49,0:29:18.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente tem dinheiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:18.20,0:29:20.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Merry tá toda arrebentada depois das viagens!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:20.90,0:29:23.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá, chefe!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:22.69,0:29:23.24,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:23.24,0:29:25.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Assim tão fácil! Então pode?!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:25.28,0:29:25.70,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:25.70,0:29:27.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então por que rasgou?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:27.70,0:29:29.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não aguento a marca de batom dela.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:29.71,0:29:32.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A vovó Kokoro e eu somos\Nvelhos companheiros de bebida.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:32.45,0:29:35.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, isso à parte, o Kaku já foi\Nfazer a avaliação.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:35.90,0:29:38.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O assunto já está em andamento. Não se preocupem.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:40.48,0:29:43.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu estava entediado hoje mesmo.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:43.01,0:29:44.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Querem um tour pelo estaleiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:44.69,0:29:46.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau! Sério?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:46.28,0:29:47.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, me sigam.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:47.39,0:29:50.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o mesmo homem que acabou\Nde cancelar todos os compromissos...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:50.35,0:29:52.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza! Vamos ver o estaleiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:53.79,0:29:55.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade. O dinheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:56.40,0:29:58.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O dinheiro...? O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:58.50,0:30:00.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? O quê? O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:00.57,0:30:02.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:03.45,0:30:06.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm? Tudo bem, Usopp?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:07.20,0:30:10.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-O-O dinheiro... O dinheiro sumiu!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:10.45,0:30:11.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:11.91,0:30:13.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Procurem em tudo!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:13.36,0:30:16.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sumiu! Não encontro em lugar nenhum!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:14.19,0:30:16.91,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Quê...? Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:17.46,0:30:18.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:18.83,0:30:21.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ali!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:27.80,0:30:31.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, seus ladrões!\NQue isso?! Quem são vocês?!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:31.31,0:30:33.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que estão levando nosso dinheiro?!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:33.90,0:30:36.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Espera!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:38.33,0:30:39.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Valeu pela grana!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:40.51,0:30:45.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devolvam nosso dinheiro!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=17}===============================DIALOGUE============================
